{
  "title": "ISic003353. Honours for L. Sempronius Atratinus",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span> L(ucio)?] Sempro[nio <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span> L(uci)? f(ilio)? A]tratin[o <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span> a]ug(uri) imp(eratori) [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[M(arcus)? Liv]ius M(arci) f(ilius) Optat[us] <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]sui <span data-text=\"hono\">hono</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>..]SEMPRO[...<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>.....]TRATIN[.<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>.]UGIMP[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[.....]IUSMFOPTAT[..]<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]SUI<span data-text=\"hono\">HONO</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003353_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003353_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003353.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003353-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text after Tansey 2008</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Originally published and restored by Cagiano de Azevedo as a dedication to a Sempronius Atratinus, perhaps son of the consul of 34 BCE, as flamen of Augusta, by the man attested in CIL 10.7501 on Gozo/Gallus. Tansey offers strong arguments in favour of reading the text instead as an honorific for the consul of 34 BC, as augur and imperator, subsequent to his triumph of 21 BCE.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 2008.0602 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a></li><li> 1969-1970.0204 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a></li><li> Cagiano de Azevedo 1969 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002107\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002107</a></li><li> Tansey 2008 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001478\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001478</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-5  17-37  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
